snippet: Prime minister Benjamin Netanyahu placed his own interests over Israel’s on issues including Iran and the Palestinian conflict, charged Yuval Diskin, the former head of the domestic security service.
abstract: Yuval Diskin, former head of Israel's internal security service, accuses Israeli Prime Min Benjamin Netanyahu of placing his own interests over Israel's on issues including Iran and the Palestinian conflict.
lead_paragraph: Prime minister Benjamin Netanyahu placed his own interests over Israel’s on issues including Iran and the Palestinian conflict, charged Yuval Diskin, the former head of the domestic security service.

headline.seo: Yuval Diskin, Former Israeli Security Chief, Calls Netanyahu a Poor Leader
headline.main: Former Israeli Security Chief Calls Netanyahu a Poor Leader
